body.p:
The following actions are available on the Expand/Collapse menu:
grid editornavigationexpand allExpand All - Expands the selection and all its children;
grid editornavigationcollapse allCollapse All - Collapses the selection and all its children;
grid editornavigationexpand childrenExpand Children - Expands all the children of the selection but not the selection;
grid editornavigationcollapse childrenCollapse Children - Collapses all the children of the selection but not the selection;
grid editornavigationcollapse othersCollapse Others - Collapses all the siblings of the current selection but not the selection.
